    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Institutions that provide training in the creation of fine and decorative arts, established primarily for the instruction of artists but often endowed with other functions, such as providing exhibition space for students and mature artists who have been accepted as members.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000050615/IFLA Glossary for Art Librarians (1984)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>提供課程以進行純藝術與裝飾藝術之訓練的教育機構，成立主要係為了培養藝術家，然而卻常具備其他用途，例如提供展覽空間，給予學生與學校單位所認可的資深藝術家。 提供課程以進行純藝術與裝飾藝術之訓練的教育機構，成立主要係為了培養藝術家，然而卻常具備其他用途，例如提供展覽空間，給予學生與學校單位所認可的資深藝術家。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Instituições que oferecem treinamento na criação de artes plásticas e decorativas, estabelecidas principalmente para a instrução de artistas, mas muitas vezes dotadas de outras funções, como proporcionar espaço de exposição para estudantes e artistas maduros que foram aceitos como membros.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000316/CVAA-BR</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
